    "en": {
      "title": "The Minister of Education traveled to France",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Education Minister Sushil Premajayan is on his way to France to attend a meeting of education ministers to be held at UNESCO headquarters.",
        "He left Katunayake Airport this morning (28) and it has been informed that the meeting will continue till the next day.",
        "The conference will focus on the educational reform of the respective countries for better education, with the goal of sustainable development of students from many countries who have lost their schooling due to the corona epidemic."
      ],
